description: The snake, named Isis, got loose in an apartment block in Rennes, terrifying residents.
title: Python escapes apartment in French city of Rennes
title_page: Python escapes apartment in French city of Rennes - BBC News
maintext: "It's scary," a teenager sat outside the block told the same paper. "And we especially don't go there, where there is a little fresh grass," he said, pointing to the green space.
